<br>
My friends and I need to kill a few BIG mobs.  One, for instance, is a lvl 55 warrior that doubles for 250 and have 32K HPs and is located in the Swamp of No Hope.  He's part of the Druid Epic Quest.<br>
<br>
If the druid lands her 2 dots (one for 1675ish and one for 900ish), and send in a pet with the taunt turned off, and then I begin nuking, what are the chances we'd be able to take it?<br>
<br>
Anyone tried these big mobs before?  It's kinda like REVERSE FEAR KITING...we're the ones running. <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->   <br>
<br>
